": [963.0, 533.3, 1000.5, 550.0]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [1063.6, 533.3, 1080.3, 550.0]}, {"text": "Unconsolidated joint venture", "bbox": [160.5, 554.1, 372.0, 570.8]}, {"text": "income . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [177.2, 575.0, 429.1, 591.7]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [487.4, 575.0, 504.1, 591.7]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [562.5, 575.0, 579.2, 591.7]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [640.9, 575.0, 657.6, 591.7]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [716.5, 575.0, 733.2, 591.7]}, {"text": "4,186", "bbox": [805.4, 575.0, 842.9, 591.7]}, {"text": "1,758", "bbox": [880.4, 575.0, 918.0, 591.7]}, {"text": "2,428", "bbox": [963.0, 575.0, 1000.5, 591.7]}, {"text": "138.11%", "bbox": [1034.5, 575.0, 1096.0, 591.7]}, {"text": "Total expenses . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [177.2, 604.2, 429.1, 620.8]}, {"text": "410,232", "bbox": [449.9, 604.2, 504.1, 620.8]}, {"text": "383,177", "bbox": [525.0, 604.2, 579.2, 620.8]}, {"text": "27,055", "bbox": [611.7, 604.2, 657.6, 620.8]}, {"text": "7.06%", "bbox": [704.0, 604.2, 748.8, 620.8]}, {"text": "734,844", "bbox": [788.7, 604.2, 842.9, 620.8]}, {"text": "652,332", "bbox": [863.8, 604.2, 918.0, 620.8]}, {"text": "82,512", "bbox": [954.7, 604.2, 1000.5, 620.8]}, {"text": "12.65%", "bbox": [1042.8, 604.2, 1096.0, 620.8]}, {"text": "Income before minority interests and", "bbox": [143.8, 633.3, 414.2, 650.0]}, {"text": "net derivative losses . . . . . . . . . . . $482,234 $438,518", "bbox": [160.5, 654.2, 579.2, 670.8]}, {"text": "$43,716", "bbox": [603.4, 654.2, 657.6, 670.8]}, {"text": "9.97%", "bbox": [704.0, 654.2, 748.8, 670.8]}, {"text": "$ 298,134 $227,021", "bbox": [767.9, 654.2, 918.0, 670.8]}, {"text": "$ 71,113", "bbox": [938.0, 654.2, 1000.5, 670.8]}, {"text": "31.32%", "bbox": [1042.8, 654.2, 1096.0, 670.8]}, {"text": "The increase in rental revenue in our Same Property Portfolio is primarily a result of an overall", "bbox": [185.5, 700.0, 1060.4, 720.8]}, {"text": "increase in rental rates on new leases and rollovers, an increase in reimbursable operating expenses as", "bbox": [143.8, 725.0, 1077.5, 745.9]}, {"text": "well as an increase in termination fees and early surrender income offset by a decrease in occupancy", "bbox": [143.8, 750.0, 1063.2, 770.9]}, {"text": "from year to year. Rental revenue is comprised of base rent, including termination fees and early", "bbox": [143.8, 775.0, 1030.9, 795.9]}, {"text": "surrender income, recoveries from tenants and parking and other. Base rental revenue is recognized on", "bbox": [143.8, 800.0, 1088.4, 820.9]}, {"text": "a straight-line basis over the terms of the respective leases. Accrued rental income represents the", "bbox": [143.8, 825.0, 1031.2, 845.9]}, {"text": "amount by which straight-line rental revenue exceeds rents currently billed in accordance with the lease", "bbox": [143.8, 850.1, 1088.7, 870.9]}, {"text": "agreements. Straight line rent for the year ended December 31, 2001 was $28.0 million compared to", "bbox": [143.8, 875.1, 1058.3, 895.9]}, {"text": "$13.1 million for the year ended December 31, 2000. Termination fees and early surrender income", "bbox": [143.8, 900.1, 1041.3, 920.9]}, {"text": "increased from $3.7 million for the year ended December 31, 2000 to $21.6 million for the year ended", "bbox": [143.8, 925.1, 1077.9, 945.9]}, {"text": "December 31, 2001. Included in the $21.6 million is $12.4 million related to the early surrender of", "bbox": [143.8, 950.1, 1041.5, 970.9]}, {"text": "space of a tenant at 875 Third Avenue, of which approximately $9.2 million has been received to date.", "bbox": [143.8, 975.1, 1080.0, 995.9]}, {"text": "We expect to receive the remaining amount on a monthly basis through July 2002. The occupancy for", "bbox": [143.8, 1000.1, 1071.6, 1020.9]}, {"text": "our Same Property Portfolio decreased from 98.9% as of December 31, 2000 to 95.8% as of", "bbox": [143.8, 1025.1, 985.4, 1045.9]}, {"text": "December 31, 2001. Additional increases in rental revenues in our total portfolio are primarily the", "bbox": [143.8, 1050.1, 1042.5, 1071.0]}, {"text": "result of rental revenues earned on properties we acquired or placed in service after January 1, 2000", "bbox": [143.8, 1075.1, 1062.8, 1096.0]}, {"text": "offset by a decrease in overall occupancy from 98.9% to 95.3%.", "bbox": [143.8, 1100.1, 724.4, 1121.0]}, {"text": "The Company has not recognized $0.4 million of rental revenue during the year ended", "bbox": [185.5, 1137.6, 977.7, 1158.5]}, {"text": "December 31, 2001, related to a tenant who has filed for bankruptcy. Although the tenant vacated the", "bbox": [143.8, 1162.6, 1078.1, 1183.5]}, {"text": "space during 2001, the rental payments, to the extent the space is not re-let, are guaranteed by a third", "bbox": [143.8, 1187.7, 1078.2, 1208.5]}, {"text": "party. Revenue of approximately $0.2 million per month relating to this space will be recognized, when", "bbox": [143.8, 1212.7, 1083.7, 1233.5]}, {"text": "and if, collection is reasonably assured.", "bbox": [143.8, 1237.7, 499.5, 1258.5]}, {"text": "The increase in development and management services income in our total portfolio is mainly due", "bbox": [185.5, 1275.2, 1084.4, 1296.0]}, {"text": "to an increase in development and management income earned on contracts starting in 2001 and 2000", "bbox": [143.8, 1300.2, 1078.1, 1321.0]}, {"text": "and an increase of approximately $0.4 million of work order profits earned on the entire portfolio. This", "bbox": [143.8, 1325.2, 1090.0, 1346.0]}, {"text": "was offset by certain management and development contracts ending in 2000 and some reductions in", "bbox": [143.8, 1350.2, 1064.7, 1371.0]}, {"text": "charges for management fees.", "bbox": [143.8, 1375.2, 414.9, 1396.1]}, {"text": "29", "bbox": [608.6, 1465.9, 629.4, 1486.7]}]}